Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这儿太好了 健二前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.74,0:02:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,树 美极了 我要燃烧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.93,0:02:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.21,0:02:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这边 一起游泳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.76,0:02:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...那个...我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 现在就来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.63,0:02:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.80,0:02:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.04,0:02:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这儿太好了 树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.03,0:02:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.35,0:02:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(138,131)\fs20\fad(650,900)}夏末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.26,0:02:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,池谷前辈也去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.19,0:02:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 不开心?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.51,0:02:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拓海 去乘滑梯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.93,0:02:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不了 我想一个人呆在这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.95,0:02:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙总是呆呆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...可以的话我们也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.59,0:03:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 顺便一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.18,0:03:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.36,0:03:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺便顺便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.63,0:03:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拓海一起去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.05,0:03:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...不了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.08,0:03:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最怕滑梯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡说什么 连那超级漂移都不在话下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.70,0:03:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙雪喜欢蛮干 她的一贯风格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那班人也很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.52,0:03:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的没关系吗 大家都请假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我硬请了带薪假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.93,0:03:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然店长一脸的不愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.84,0:03:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太耀眼了 现在仍觉得心脏快裂开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.07,0:03:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是看到了真子的泳装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.36,0:03:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就已经是二十一年的人生中最棒的夏日回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一生都忘不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.00,0:04:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正对我来说真子是高不可攀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.42,0:04:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,池谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.81,0:04:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多事真的要多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.69,0:04:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真心感谢池谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.08,0:04:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经过上次比赛我明白了很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.77,0:04:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.46,0:04:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然给你添了不少麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我决定不放弃赛车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.64,0:04:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.56,0:04:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想你放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.11,0:04:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自命不凡罢了 什么碓冰山道最快 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.41,0:04:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是别人捧出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.63,0:04:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 拉不回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用侧滑避开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.37,0:05:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那场比赛中 我重新认识到控车技术的深奥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.58,0:05:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我明白现在放弃的话就等于半途而废
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.60,0:05:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听你这么说我就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.97,0:05:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做的事也算起了点作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.41,0:05:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,池谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.20,0:05:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得上次在湖畔的约定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不太会说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.99,0:05:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以池谷先生可能有点误会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.79,0:05:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说的并不是想做交易的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.31,0:05:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请要了我的处女吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.91,0:05:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八点左右在初次和池谷先生相遇的招牌下等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.36,0:06:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再慢一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.78,0:06:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.18,0:06:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背后的胸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.22,0:06:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健二前辈...背后居然是个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.31,0:06:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太悲哀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.82,0:06:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子 拿一下球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.81,0:06:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高桥凉介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我扔了 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.56,0:07:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往哪儿扔啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.61,0:07:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.95,0:07:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.78,0:07:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么真子有高桥凉介的照片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.23,0:07:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...能问个问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.71,0:07:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.07,0:07:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说过以前没和人交往过吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.45,0:07:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算没交往过 爱的人总有的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.85,0:08:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想为什么没和他交往呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.46,0:08:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得真子这么可爱的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.23,0:08:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝大多数男人都会趋之若鹜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.24,0:08:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会...哪有这种事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.63,0:08:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是做什么的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.72,0:08:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人...是车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.22,0:08:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时我还是高中生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.88,0:08:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概三年前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.04,0:08:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和几位前辈去看赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.84,0:08:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时的我一无所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.08,0:08:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶然间被一辆车的跑法给震撼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.94,0:08:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人的跑法 连我这外行都看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和别的车不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有这么酷的事情 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.20,0:08:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是就完全陷入了车手的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.99,0:09:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上去考了驾照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.85,0:09:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还硬是买了辆车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.31,0:09:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是忘我的练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.71,0:09:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想着开得好的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.92,0:09:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能稍微接近那人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动机不纯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.65,0:09:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看那人的跑法 所以坚持去看比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.14,0:09:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可和那人连话都没说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.75,0:09:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己都不知道那算不算恋爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.85,0:09:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不清楚思慕的到底他的人还是他的跑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你是爱他的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.88,0:10:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.48,0:10:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾经的最爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.65,0:10:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 这种痛楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 不问就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真子离我好遥远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子一直思慕的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然是群马地区NO.1的超级巨星...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.58,0:10:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高桥凉介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.58,0:10:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.48,0:10:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她向往的车会是FC
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.65,0:10:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了 不可能赢得了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.01,0:11:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥终于要出手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.43,0:11:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和那辆秋名的86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.07,0:11:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪我试试如何? 启介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.49,0:11:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的最快理论 实践给你看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.75,0:11:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.77,0:11:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开心的一塌糊涂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.82,0:11:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和女孩去游泳原来这么开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.28,0:11:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.58,0:11:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是几乎都和健二前辈在一起吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.02,0:12:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子和沙雪是最棒的呢 前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还真会见风使舵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.12,0:12:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前阵子不是还在说车手不需要女人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.97,0:12:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们俩不一样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们俩穿比基尼的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使灼伤了眼也不舍得移开啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太耀眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.64,0:12:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不舍得沙雪那晃动的咪咪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.46,0:12:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但还是真子好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.16,0:12:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身材出众 对吧 池谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.42,0:12:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这心不在焉的反应算什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.42,0:12:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得你有点郁闷 和真子吵架了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.10,0:12:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事 只是有点累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.05,0:13:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这时候来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.76,0:13:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 店长 今天硬是请了假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.67,0:13:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 你还年轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也该挥洒一下青春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年纪不小了别光沉迷于车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都担心你找不到女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.95,0:13:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.54,0:13:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的天使是叫真子吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺利吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.12,0:13:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...看来是不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.84,0:13:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是高攀不起啊 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么丧气话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.07,0:13:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 池谷 女人其实...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.50,0:13:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别...真的没关系了店长 我已经放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能赢得过高桥凉介啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.31,0:14:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事? 总算是追上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥的FC明明没改动过 为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.91,0:14:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的最快理论...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.53,0:14:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入了新的数据就能进化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.79,0:14:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等着吧 秋名的86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.65,0:14:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个理论完成之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是将你名字列入失败者名单之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.48,0:15:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好难受 心跳得太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.00,0:15:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办? 现在就已经这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,池谷先生来了的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.76,0:15:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.88,0:15:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋啊 池谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.59,0:15:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对女人一无所知啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.46,0:15:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.13,0:15:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别呃了 听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.97,0:15:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果以前交往的是高桥凉介那就另当别论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.79,0:15:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种事只要是小女孩都有过的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.64,0:15:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和思慕电视里的演员没什么区别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.55,0:15:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静头脑想一想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.79,0:15:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因为真子选择的并非高桥凉介而是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表示她拿出勇气下的决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.15,0:15:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为相信你才会毫不隐瞒地说出那种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.51,0:15:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不懂吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.19,0:15:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别总是执迷于你那无聊的自卑感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.20,0:16:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恋慕就是要包容对方的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.62,0:16:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的爱与恋不正是如此吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 八点?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.27,0:16:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 已经过了三十分钟啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不可能了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.16,0:16:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么狂飙去横川也要一小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.62,0:16:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子不可能还等着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.78,0:16:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种事不去怎么知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不去的话就炒了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.38,0:17:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使劲飙 池谷 你也是个车手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.11,0:17:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候才需要拼命地跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.60,0:17:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说...来不及了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.19,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是青春啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.09,0:17:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长说得对 我实在太笨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.07,0:17:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子这么好的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.15,0:17:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死也不会再有机会遇上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.47,0:17:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么不坦率点呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.52,0:17:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫佐藤真子 打我电话哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.28,0:18:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把处女献给池谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.16,0:18:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八点左右在初次和池谷先生相遇的招牌下等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子一直都是认真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.50,0:18:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我...而我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.27,0:18:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个大混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.95,0:18:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脚开始痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌凉鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.03,0:19:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子 我并不怎么想去旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.73,0:19:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扪心自问...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想什么呢 不是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.83,0:19:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何我只想见到真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.79,0:19:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 求求你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.41,0:19:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再给我一次机会 别将我的天使带离人间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.06,0:19:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堵车? 出事故了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.69,0:19:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.95,0:19:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会...神啊...你怎么能这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.33,0:20:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.00,0:20:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不穿凉鞋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.60,0:24:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了拓海 那束花是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.31,0:24:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.32,0:24:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏木送的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.19,0:24:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.69,0:24:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.58,0:24:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,观众女孩送给如今群马车手中无人不知...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.58,0:24:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开着藤原豆腐店(自家用)熊猫TRUENO拓海的礼物吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.34,0:24:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.33,0:24:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是沙雪了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.90,0:24:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙雪很奇怪地看中了拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.49,0:24:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是高桥凉介送来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.78,0:24:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回 头文字D 来自超级巨星的挑战书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.00,0:24:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别错过
